added.title: Thomas' Day Off
added.description: When all the trains but Thomas get deliveries, he's left to spend the day alone. With the help of an old boxcar and a battered beachball... an adventure unfolds.
added.originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

added.title: The Real Number One
added.description: When Thomas' #1 is covered by paint, he sets out to prove to himself that he is still number one, but when everything starts to go wrong for him, he learns what it really means to be #1.
added.originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

added.title: Caillou's Gym Day/Our Rocket Ship/Caillou Helps Grandpa/The Backyard Bowlers/Caillou's Milk Run
added.description: Caillou gets a special invitation to go to André's gym class./Caillou and Leo are playing with their rocket ships in the park./On a winter day, Dad and Caillou go over to Grandpa's with their skates./When Caillou and Rosie stay at Grandma and Grandpa's house, Grandpa uses pop bottles and a rubber ball to create a kid's bowling alley./Caillou accidentally spills the rest of the milk before Rosie could get her cereal.

added.title: Dancing at Grandma's/Mystery Valentine/Play Ball!/Dogsled Ahead!
added.description: It is a rainy day and Caillou is disappointed because he will not be able to go play at the park with Grandma./It's Valentine's day and Caillou is invited to a Valentine's party at his best friend Leo's house./When Dad's baseball team, the Tigers, are playing a game at the park, Caillou, Rosie and Mom go to cheer him on./Caillou and his family are heading to the tobogganing hill!

added.title: Caillou's Sleepover Guest/Games in the Park/The Sugar Shack/Winter Mystery/Caillou's Snowday
added.description: Leo is spending the night at Caillou's./Caillou is excited when Miss Martin takes him and his friends to the park for some special activities./When Caillou's family makes a springtime visit to Jonas' ranch, he takes them on a sleigh ride./The twins, Jason and Jeffrey, have come to play with Caillou in the snow./When Caillou, Rosie and Mom head to the big park, Caillou sees André.

added.title: Caillou's Favorite Plate/Fun in the Mud/All Aboard!/I Scream for Ice Cream/Gilbert's House
added.description: Grandma has given Caillou a special spaceship plate./It's raining outside but there is no stopping Caillou!/After finding a photograph of a four-year-old Dad with a model train set, Caillou and Dad decide to look for it./When Caillou spots a dog house outside he gets the idea that Gilbert might like a house of his own./Caillou, Rosie and Mom are having fun at the park when the ice-cream man comes around.

added.title: Super Caillou!/Trip on the Subway/Caillou's Race/As Good as New/I, Robot
added.description: Caillou just loves his Superbear storybook./Caillou learns to deal with a change in plans when Daddy has to use the car./Caillou is playing a board game with Mom and he gets a little upset./Caillou learns about 'recycling' -- literally!/ When Sarah shows Caillou and Leo her new remote controlled robot, the boys get a great idea to be robots too!

added.title: Giving
added.description: It's Sula's birthday! Bing is choosing the perfect present for her, but really loves it himself. Will Bing keep the present for himself?

added.title: Hula Hoop
added.description: Coco is showing Bing her new Holly Hula Hoop, but will be Bing be able to hula like Coco?

added.title: Big Boots
added.description: Bing and Sula are being giants and splashing in puddles with their rainy boots. What will happen when Bing finds a big puddle?

added.title: Bubbles
added.description: Bing and Pando are learning how to make bubbles, but will Bing be able to blow his own bubble?

added.title: Mushpot's Treasure
added.description: When Mushpot wishes he could roll back the seasons and relive being a Mushler, our friends get him to hang out doing cool Mushler stuff. But this just shows that Mushpot is no longer able to do all those things. Sigh! However, when our friends find a map that points to a treasure he buried when he was a Mushler, Mushpot realises it's just the Mushler experience he needed.

added.title: One Wise Bear
added.description: The Bears become lost in the Valley of Whispering Winds, where voices whisper in their ears and make them lose faith in themselves. Racing to their rescue, Tenderheart leads them to the only one who knows the antidote to the words of the Winds: a mysterious old bear of great wisdom who teaches them a valuable lesson about listening to your heart.

added.title: Shine, Lilit, Shine
added.description: The Beacon Mushroom that guides the Mushables back to Mushton in the dark has gone out. So Lilit lights up and stands in its place for the night and soon gets quite bored! Lilit's good deed has her regretting her gift she's basically just a lamp! But when her light goes out, Lilit instantly regrets regretting it: she wants her gift back!

added.title: House Flies Don't Dance/Flying the Nest/The Insult
added.description: Lucas and Maizie help Findley learn to dance./ Arlo believes he's a big owl now, so it's time to fly his nest. But is Arlo ready to leave his friends behind?/ When Lucas calls Findley a mean name, he tries to make things right again.

added.title: I'll Do it in a Minute/Cloud Gazing/Don't Do That Arlo
added.description: Arlo has fun playing, but he procrastinates when it comes to tidying up./ Lucas, Arlo, and Findley have a day of make-believe with the clouds./ Arlo can't resist the temptation to look into next door's garden through a knothole.

added.title: Storytime
added.description: It's bath time and Bing's reading his favourite story. When the book falls in the bath, how will Bing read the story?

added.title: The Sandman Is Coming
added.description: Daffy thinks the Sandman is a monster that throws sand in children's eyes.

added.title: Some Assembly Required
added.description: Bugs gets a new toy with assembly required and has to learn to follow instructions.

added.title: Dibble's Dust-Up
added.description: Grumpy's determination to get the Cloudseeker clean is comically thwarted when Dibble befriends a stowaway trio of cute dust bunnies.

added.title: Fussy Duck
added.description: Pato, fresh from his shower, is determined to keep clean. Pocoyo and Elly have very different ideas, and Pato soon realizes that half the fun of getting clean is getting dirty in the first place!

added.title: A Dog's Life
added.description: Pocoyo pretends to be an elephant, a duck and a dog - but when Loula needs his help, Pocoyo sees that sometimes it's best just to be himself.

added.title: Pocoyolympics
added.description: Pocoyo, Elly and Pato stage their own version of the olympics - with a funny and very original variety of contests.

added.title: Picture This
added.description: Pocoyo imagines that fish live in different places and draws funny pictures for his friends.

added.title: Whale's Birthday
added.description: It's Whale's birthday. When all of Whale's presents get spoiled on the way to the party, Pocoyo, Elly and Pato are sad. But Whale is happy just to see them. Friends are what you need for a party!

removed.title: Flush Hour
removed.description: The babies learn the purpose of toilets.

removed.title: Three Cheers for Cheer
removed.description: When hard-working Cheer exhausts her crew running a string of drills to protect a Whiffle orchard from possible emergencies, Share's belly badge accidentally creates two Cheer duplicates. Cheer takes a recreation break, unaware that her clones are working Share and the crew - who think they're the real Cheer - even harder.

removed.description: Caillou's crayons are all worn down or broken, so Mommy suggests a trip to the store for some new ones./Caillou's playschool is on a special field trip to an apple orchard./Halloween is coming and it's time to pick out a costume to wear.

removed.description: Pocoyo wants to play 'pitch and putt' like his friends, Pocoyo and Elly, but he can't quite get the hang of it. He watches carefully and finally grasps where he was going wrong.

removed.title: Elly's Big Chase
removed.description: Elly inadvertently sets off on a fantastic journey - all the while fast asleep on her chair - as Pocoyo and Pato protect her from danger.

removed.title: Pocoyo, Pocoyo
removed.description: Pocoyo discovers a fabulous new playmate - his echoooo-ooo-ooo-ooo!

removed.description: Caillou accompanies Mom to the grocery store./When Caillou, Grandpa and Daddy go on a canoe trip, Caillou gets to see some wild animals./On an autumn day, Caillou and his Mommy take a walk and pass by a construction site./When Dad's burning toasts trigger the fire alarm, he decides it is the perfect opportunity to practice a fire drill./Caillou and his Mommy are finishing preparing a picnic lunch.
